snippet.title: Fretless - Save & Sound 2024 performance
snippet.description:
Enjoy some good Fretless rock music with Rob Scallon and Jeff Linville! 

Fretless is a turned-based RPG where you wield powerful legendary instruments, gather mighty riff attacks, and save the land from Rick Riffson's devilish goons and musical hybrid monsters!

Wishlist Fretless on Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/2429050/Fretless__The_Wrath_of_Riffson/
